thread.title: Bill & Brenda Moore
thread.title_full: MirrorMate Frames reviewed by Bill & Brenda Moore

author: Bill & Brenda Moore
title: Bill & Brenda Moore
text: Over ten years, I've bought MirrorMate Frames on four different occasions and I have always been happy with the product. I once did my own frame to save money but it did not have the beauty or ease of implementation I experienced with MirrorMate. So I will always go back to MirrorMate.
